videos.description: Boise State's Jabril Frazier wraps up Oklahoma State QB Taylor Cornelius for a sack.
videos.headline: Boise's D comes up with a big sack

videos.description: Boise State's Brett Rypien tosses a deep ball that is hauled in by John Hightower for a diving 31-yard touchdown against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Hightower flies through the air on diving TD catch

videos.description: Taylor Cornelius finds Tylan Wallace on a 43-yard strike to set up Justice Hill's 8-yard touchdown run, tying Oklahoma State's game vs. Boise State
videos.headline: Big Oklahoma State pass sets up 8-yard TD

videos.description: Boise State's punt is blocked by Oklahoma State to set up the Cowboys' offense close to the goal line.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State blocks punt to set up great field position

videos.description: Taylor Cornelius takes it himself for a 1-yard touchdown run to give Oklahoma State the lead over Boise State.
videos.headline: OSU's Cornelius smashes in 1-yard TD

videos.description: A.J. Richardson  makes a nice one-handed catch en route to a 34-yard Boise State touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State's Richardson only needs one hand for unbelievable TD

videos.description: OSU's Taylor Cornelius finds Dillon Stoner crossing the middle for a quick 32-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Stoner outruns Boise State for 32-yard TD

videos.description: Boise State's Brett Rypien rockets a 5-yard touchdown pass to Chase Blakley on fourth down to keep Broncos in the game.
videos.headline: Blakley snags a big 4th-down TD catch for Boise State

videos.description: Taylor Cornelius pushes his way in for a 6-yard touchdown to give Oklahoma State a 23-point lead over Boise State late in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: OSU's Cornelius calls his own number for TD run
